stateDiagram-v2
  [*] --> Queued: QDMA insert task_list
  Queued --> Binding: BDMA picks idle HCQD
  Binding --> Executing: write MCQD_ADDR + BINDDMA_HCQDID
  Executing --> StopRequested: exc_cnt == 0 and release needed
  StopRequested --> StopWaiting: HCQD/User not stopped yet
  StopRequested --> Releasing: stop complete immediately
  StopWaiting --> Releasing: HCQD_STATUS + CPE_FW_HCQD_STOPPED ready
  Releasing --> Idle: RELEASE_HCQDID set then cleared
  Idle --> [*]
